{"tid":419960,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"學神載2女狂飆150km/h　逃捕4公里插欄被捕","createTime":"2017-10-01T03:45:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-01T15:07:02.000Z","uid":81228,"like":58,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":100,"replies":[{"pid":"937c61c13e4c61b650cea638e60aa688153433c9","tid":419960,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T03:45:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171001/photo/bkn-20171001021218760-1001_00822_001_01b.jpg?20171001112444\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171001%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171001021218760-1001_00822_001_01b.jpg%3F20171001112444&h=038fae13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n思域失控撞欄剷上行人路停下，(小圖)被捕男司機。(胡德威攝)<br />\n<br />\n新界北交通執行及管制組特遣隊「隱形戰車」在區內巡邏，至凌晨1時許，警員於大埔吐露港往上水方向近白石角對開，發現一輛本田思域與一輛白色Audi「鍊車」，時速一度高達150公里，思域期間左穿右插，「隱形戰車」一直尾隨監視。當2車駛至粉嶺和合石附近分道揚鑣，其中一車迅速失去蹤影，思域則繼續高速於馬會道與馬適路交界燈位停下等候；警員遂亮起警示燈號及示意司機停車受查，惟思域見狀高速逃走，「戰車」啣尾追截。思域沿馬會道向文錦渡高速駛去，警車亦緊隨其後，雙方追逐約4公里後，當思域轉入寶運路時，失控直插路邊行人路鐵欄，約5米鐵欄損毀。思域零件飛脫四散路上。車上男司機及2名女乘客並無受傷，3人趁機落車逃走。<br />\n<br />\n「隱形戰車」上2名警員見狀亦落車，兵分兩路追截，其中一名警員窮追200米，終在附近一條村擒獲涉案司機；負責駕駛「戰車」的警長，亦將2名女乘客喝停，3人被帶上警車查問。經調查後，發現姓黃（31歲）司機僅持有學牌，他涉嫌危險駕駛、違反學習駕駛執照規定駕駛、沒有第三保下駕駛汽車、駕駛未有登記車輛、駕駛時沒有攜帶駕駛執照及未能出示身份證明文件被捕。此外，黃亦涉嫌違反感化令被通緝。2名分別姓陳（16歲）及姓周（17歲）少女，亦被帶返警署協助調查。案件由大埔警區刑事調查隊跟進。<br />\n<br />\n警員檢查思域私家車，發現匙膽未有車匙，疑曾被改動裝置，由於意外後引擎仍然開著，警員需用鉸剪插入匙膽才能將引擎關閉。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，有人透過手機交友程式認識2女，2人為同班同學，昨晚首次約會，聲稱準備前往唱卡拉OK，惟在公路上遇到Audi時即興「鍊車」，期間在公路上左穿右插被「隱形戰車」發現。<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171001/photo/bkn-20171001021218760-1001_00822_001_02b.jpg?20171001112444\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171001%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171001021218760-1001_00822_001_02b.jpg%3F20171001112444&h=5b91073b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n車上2名女乘客助查。(胡德威攝)<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171001/photo/bkn-20171001021218760-1001_00822_001_03b.jpg?20171001112444\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171001%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171001021218760-1001_00822_001_03b.jpg%3F20171001112444&h=dab4621c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n思域私家車懷疑失控撞欄。(胡德威攝)<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171001/photo/bkn-20171001021218760-1001_00822_001_04b.jpg?20171001112444\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171001%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171001021218760-1001_00822_001_04b.jpg%3F20171001112444&h=ebac556b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n男司機被捕。(胡德威攝)<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171001/photo/bkn-20171001021218760-1001_00822_001_05b.jpg?20171001112444\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171001%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171001021218760-1001_00822_001_05b.jpg%3F20171001112444&h=6a89304c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n思域於寶運路失事撞毀。(胡德威攝)<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171001/photo/bkn-20171001021218760-1001_00822_001_06b.jpg?20171001112444\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171001%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171001021218760-1001_00822_001_06b.jpg%3F20171001112444&h=32979964&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警員需用剪刀插入匙膽才能將引擎關閉。(胡德威攝)<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171001/photo/bkn-20171001021218760-1001_00822_001_07b.jpg?20171001112444\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171001%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171001021218760-1001_00822_001_07b.jpg%3F20171001112444&h=b3b2fc43&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警員在場調查。(胡德威攝)<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171001/photo/bkn-20171001021218760-1001_00822_001_08b.jpg?20171001112444\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171001%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171001021218760-1001_00822_001_08b.jpg%3F20171001112444&h=50a7f78a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n車上零件飛脫。(胡德威攝)<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171001/photo/bkn-20171001021218760-1001_00822_001_09b.jpg?20171001112444\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171001%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171001021218760-1001_00822_001_09b.jpg%3F20171001112444&h=d18292ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n車廂內放有勞工手套及工具。(胡德威攝)<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171001/bkn-20171001021218760-1001_00822_001.html?refer=hn2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171001%2Fbkn-20171001021218760-1001_00822_001.html%3Frefer%3Dhn2&d=XUAhxXaV0m5RKfaY%2BxtZ%2Fr%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=29d54db2\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171001/bkn-20171001021218760-1001_00822_001.html?refer=hn2</a>"},{"pid":"4fee67025f9221adad971106144bd012468d76f7","tid":419960,"uid":26474,"like":83,"dislike":1,"score":82,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T03:47:44.000Z","msg":"警員需用剪刀插入匙膽才能將引擎關閉<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37e37f6a83fac29f671ffd0531d54eecaf94ef63","tid":419960,"uid":8951,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T03:47:48.000Z","msg":"學神又開唔到齋"},{"pid":"9559fb5207e76aef82799ae47dbf98bcefcb64ad","tid":419960,"uid":134462,"like":46,"dislike":0,"score":46,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T03:49:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3b5d7187e7f0c20205109ea1461d3e3b9ce9b6fe","tid":419960,"uid":55913,"like":2,"dislike":18,"score":-16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T03:50:10.000Z","msg":"P牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95a004251623cc0744c8b67e2cfe2a553dd7d634","tid":419960,"uid":28802,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T03:50:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/1KoxgEEnWHw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F1KoxgEEnWHw&d=XUAhxXaV0m5RKfaY%2BxtZ%2F